# Bashkortostan, Askinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Bashkortostan (; , Ba≈üqortostan) is a rural locality (a village) in Kazanchinsky Selsoviet, Askinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 45 as of 2010. There is 1 street.
Geography
It is located 40&nbsp;km from Askino and 5&nbsp;km from Starye Kazanchi.
